                       @{"  -=> RETURN TO CONTENTS!<=-  " link contents}
@endnode


@node IML-4 " MSG-4  Subject: Digimax!
@toc contents

Subject: Digimax!
Date:    Wednesday, 02 November 1994 09:56:38 
From:    Douglas Rudd <rudd@plk.af.mil>


  ----------------------------------------------------------------------------  


It's here.....

I got home just in time to get the candy for the trick-or-treaters when
the door bell rings. It's this big, ugly trick-or-treater with a big box.
He gave me the box, I gave him a candy bar.

I'm reading the manual. More to follow.

BTW this is the third time I've tried to send this out. something is amiss
with the host at my end...

Doug Rudd
rudd@plk.af.mil
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
The Amiga Guide to the Galaxy refers to Commodore's management as
"A bunch of mindless jerks who will be the first to be lined up
against the wall and shot when the revolution comes."
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
They will get my Amiga from me when they pry it from my cold, dead hands.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------



