On Sun, 6 Nov 1994, Mr. Scott Krehbiel; ACS (PC) wrote:

> 
> Hi 
> I need to render some images to be output through a toaster.
> (yes, using Imagine, not LightWave)
> Does anyone know the proper resolution and aspect ratio for this??
