> 
>      How many of you SGI people have 2 or 3  SGI computers at your homes?

Got me here. Only two Amigas and a pc. If I pick the right six numbers,
then I'll get one - no rich relatives.
> 
>      How many highschool kids can start 3D in their homes? ( they
