Actually, silcon is one of the most common elements in the Earth's crust ;-)
 
> 
> P.S. Please don't compare it to cars, computers fanatics are not cars 
> fanatics.
>
Speak for yourself. I have more than one interest in life, and I can get
fanatical about several of them.  Cars, people, computers, politics, 
geology, physics, camping, travel, art, music, etc..... Do you have any 
other interests? Well, english grammar isn't one of them, right?
 
>            How do you come back from 3D ?
> Ayalon M. Hermony      Internet: ila2024@datasrv.co.il
> 
