  ----------------------------------------------------------------------------  


If you can get the frames converted to tga, try Dave's Targa Animator.  
It coverts frames to an fli or flc file.

Check any simtel mirror such as ftp.cdrom.com, /.2/simtel/msdos/animate 
directory.  The file is dta18g-3.zip.  

You are probably going to need a commercial product to make avi's 
(someone please let us know if there's a pd utility that will do it).

