Subject: Re: Sway effect?
Date:    Tuesday, 22 November 1994 09:15:44 
From:    Charles Blaquiere <blaq@io.org>


  ----------------------------------------------------------------------------  


As I remember, Sway is applied to the parent of a group. It will not 
affect the parent, but every child will acquire the swaying motion.


